Treasury 30-Year Bond Extends Loss After Bernanke Comments

-- B y   D a v e   L i e d t k a
-- 
2011-10-04T14:51:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/treasury-30-year-bond-extends-loss-after-bernanke-comments.html
Treasury 30-year bonds extended
losses after Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S. Bernanke  said the
central bank stands ready to take additional steps to boost U.S.
growth and cautioned lawmakers against budget moves that would
harm a “sluggish” recovery.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
